HEADWORD: Firearm
<hw>Fire"arm`</hw> <pr>(f⟦imac⟧r"⟦aum⟧rm`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
gun, pistol, or any weapon from which a shot is discharged by the force
of an explosive substance, as gunpowder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

